    Fix typo in alsaplayer style

mercredi 21 aoùt 2019
  fvwm/decorations/Amiga/*: remove non necessary spaces and lines
  asciidoc/KeyboardBindings: add words about keyboard modifiers change
  with the preferences.
  asciidoc/FAQ: fix glitches in man page.

vendredi 16 août 2019
  desktop/FVWM-Crystal_Styles: introduce a schedule for applications Styles
  to work after a Restart.
  functions/CustomButtonBar-Menu: add preference for toggle on top on same border.
  bin/fvwm-crystal.apps: added some comments.
  bin/fvwm-crystal.generate-menu: I am sick and tired to get all the crap from
  buggy software into ~/.errors.fvwm-crystal. Add a 2>/dev/null redirection
  to silent them.
  Applications/*/*: Silent the existing application launchers.
  styles/Applications-Icons-22-32: remove the comments that creates fvwm warnings

jeudi 15 août 2019
  bin/fvwm-crystal.apps, bin/fvwm-crystal.wallpaper,
  scripts/FvwmMPD/*.py: bump to python3

mercredi 14 août 2019
  functions/Media, functions/Music-*: add Cadence support, fix qjackctl menu
  when qjackctl is not installed, add Hide/Show GUI into all the buttonless menu.

mardi 13 août 2019
+ ~japa~Japa in application database.
  desktop/HVWM-Crystal-Styles: append Generated--Applications-Icons-22-32
  functions: remove media players icon styles
  bin/fvwm-crystal.generate-menu: Introduce Icon and MiniIcon styles generation,
  fix for non probable spaces in desktop files.
  styles/Applications-Icons-22-32: add media players icon styles
  functions/Fullscreen: bump to fvwm native Maximize Fullscreen

jeudi 5 juin 2019
  recipes/lap*: fix pager X11 geometry string.
  recipes/Wing-Commander, recipes/Default: fix font
  recipes/*, functions/LoadCommonStuffs : fix missing variables at startup by moving
  set_DestopIconsGeom call to the recipes.

mercredi 5 juin 2019
  scripts/desktop_manager: fix wrong redirection
  fvwm/config: comment Welcome line, it's a debug stuff
  bin/fvwm-crystal: comment debug lines

lundi 14 mai 2019
  addons/*.pot: update to current state of fvwm-crystal
  locale/fr_FR.UTF-8/LC_MESSAGES/fvwm-crystal.*o: translate new and missing strings

